---
import VersionCards from './VersionCards.astro';
import YouTubePlaylistEmbed from './YouTubePlaylistEmbed.astro';
import { releaseFamilies } from '../lib/releaseData';

const rawBase = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const base = rawBase.endsWith('/') ? rawBase : `${rawBase}/`;
---

<section class="ap-home-shell">
  <div class="ap-home-copy">
    <p class="ap-kicker">Automatic Pro</p>
    <p class="ap-home-line">
      Automatic Pro is a profile family built to automate puck saturation and extraction with clever phase stops.
    </p>
    <details class="ap-home-details">
      <summary class="ap-home-details-summary">What is the idea behind Automatic Pro?</summary>
      <div class="ap-home-details-copy">
        <p>
          Automatic Pro is designed as a universal profile family. Instead of creating different profiles for different
          beans, it aims to let taste be shaped mainly through the classic variables: preparation, grind size,
          temperature, and yield, similar to a traditional 9 bar profile.
        </p>
        <p>
          What makes it different is its adaptive behavior. Rather than relying on hard-coded phase lengths, it uses
          machine feedback such as pressure and flow to adjust the phases automatically. The result is a profile that
          responds more consistently to user input, mistakes, and intended changes, while reducing unnecessary profile
          tweaking and keeping the focus on the factors that shape flavor.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>

  <figure class="ap-photo-card">
    <img alt="Espresso in a cup" class="ap-photo-card-image" src={`${base}images/espresso.jpg`} />
  </figure>
</section>

<VersionCards families={releaseFamilies} />

<YouTubePlaylistEmbed
  playlistId="PLU3cLYAfI4Q7Z_nKsWah8Is_W156wTLRq"
  title="Automatic Pro video playlist"
  videoId="U2aFZWOsT5w"
/>

<p class="ap-home-note">
  Discussion on
  <a href="https://discord.com/invite/3JcR5csD4E" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank">GaggiMate Discord</a>.
</p>
